{"tid":2286281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華盛頓有集會支持特朗普，拜登稱接近完成組建管治班子","createTime":"2020-11-15T00:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T00:51:01.000Z","uid":278587,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2ebc8557df1a0a893a1cc709b9c016bec46023d0","tid":2286281,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T00:21:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560058-20201115.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560058-20201115.htm&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=b95fae2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560058-20201115.htm&h=99cd23d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560058-20201115.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n大批聲援美國總統特朗普的民眾，在首都華盛頓集會及遊行，支持特朗普陣營所指大選出現舞弊的說法。集會有多個主題，包括停止盜取選票及令美國再次強大等，都是特朗普社交專頁常見的留言；參與遊行的包括部分極右團體人士。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普陣營一直宣稱大選有涉及選票的欺詐行為，並在部分關鍵州份打法律戰。報道指特朗普無實質證據，在各州提出的訴訟至今亦未見成功。特朗普離開白宮前往打高爾夫球時，有民眾向車隊揮動旗幟，高叫做多4年等口號；而在球場外有反對者展示標語，內容是我們已投票，你已被解僱。<br />\n<br />\n獲主流傳媒推算取得足夠選舉人票當選的民主黨拜登說，已接近完成組建管治班子。"},{"pid":"9b4a7edf1e077b3d14ae013d6f46b6ac0b2fa006","tid":2286281,"uid":222614,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T00:42:57.000Z","msg":"咁心急，入到監倉先組都未遲 ...."},{"pid":"60ed3aa65b30aed82e9c2c33f7f72873f5dd3b18","tid":2286281,"uid":218407,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b4a7edf1e077b3d14ae013d6f46b6ac0b2fa006","tid":2286281,"uid":222614,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T00:42:57.000Z","msg":"咁心急，入到監倉先組都未遲 ...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T00:47:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542df5ad3f5cbef6b18ed11d1d9612836d609ab8","tid":2286281,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T00:48:13.000Z","msg":"拜登話接近完成組建班子單嘢 FC咗未？"},{"pid":"c72d1458a5208f0d271669093b621a3cea7b0386","tid":2286281,"uid":160373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9b4a7edf1e077b3d14ae013d6f46b6ac0b2fa006","tid":2286281,"uid":222614,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T00:42:57.000Z","msg":"咁心急，入到監倉先組都未遲 ...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T00:51:01.000Z","msg":"死咗先組啦<br />\n咁多死人投票比佢<br />\n應該落到去先做總統"}]}